  <bioghist id="aspace_9983b15d7d23378baea61ae2173388c1">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Donald Holcomb served as Director of the Cornell Laboratory of Atomic and Solid State Physics from 1964-1968 and Chairman of the Department of Physics from 1969-1974 and 1982-1986.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_33c7fec03d94a282485e48515652c97c">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Correspondence, lab notebooks, research and subject files on electron paramagnetic resonance, and experimental data pertaining to Holcomb's work at Cornell in the Dept. of Physics and in the Laboratory of Atomic and Solid State Physics.</p>  </scopecontent>
